title: Best magazine build
review:
Opening;

This AAT is very good and we'll built and accurate for its size and price .

The build-

The wide base is well built and the spine is sloped vet well and has two cannons on the sides and the engine detail on each side is also good . The head is well built and has the hatch detail and the main cannon unlike the 2020 version is the appropriate length .

In conclusion-

this is an incredible build with the techniques and accuracy being really good I would recommend it to any Lego star wars fan .
